          "field_id": "if_the_biopsy_was_performed_for_a_benign_lesion_and_the_dcis_is_an_incidental_finding_this_should_be",
          "label": "If the biopsy was performed for a benign lesion and the DCIS is an incidental finding, this should be documented. An example would be the finding of DCIS in an excision for a palpable fibroadenoma. In some cases, other pathologic findings are important for the clinical management of patients.",
